"struct:4d901aa9f9a28864b6c4893dfacffe76"
"struct"
"sqliteAlterApplier"
"sqliteAlterApplier"
"schema_modifier.go"
"go"
128
133
5
1
"sqliteAlterApplier implements ddl.Applier for the in-flight\nAlterCollection transaction. One instance per AlterCollection call.\nEmbeds the transaction so each ApplyXxx method runs against the\nsame *sql.Tx as the rest of the batch — rollback on any error\nundoes the whole batch.\n\nctx is stored only as a fallback for the rare case an ApplyXxx\ncaller does not forward the per-call ctx (which the current\nAlterOp.ApplyTo contract always does); per-call ctx wins where\nsupplied."
""
