"struct:e25359329adf3ade391cace27d185750"
"struct"
"Database"
"Database"
"database.go"
"go"
34
40
5
1
"Database is the dalgo2sqlite driver instance. It implements\n[dal.DB] by delegating to an inner [dal.DB] obtained from\n[dalgo2sql.NewDatabase], and adds SQLite-specific dbschema, ddl,\nand concurrency surfaces.\n\nConstruct via [NewDatabase]. Database values are safe for\nconcurrent use only insofar as SQLite itself is — readers can be\nconcurrent under WAL mode; writers serialize."
""
